race.comment: OH DEER (7) has come back much stronger this campaign and looks well placed today. Ran on late when a game third over 1350m at Wyong. Can sit off this lot and pick them up effortlessly with the senior rider booked. LISTINS LASS (1) just over a month between runs when a respectable sixth over 1250m at Newcastle in a BM64 behind Oui Oui Oui. Back in grade and will be doing her best work late. PRORATA (3) failed to stretch out on the firm surface when a battling twelfth over this journey at Kembla Grange. Will find his easier and stays in the mix. OUR LADY STARDUST (9) has a poor win record, and the tongue-tie goes on. Gets in light with the claim and can sneak into the minor money.
